        <p>
          The platform's design philosophy prioritizes adaptability without sacrificing credibility. ESG Credits follows the ICMA framework's structure, logic, and principles, yet remains flexible enough to work with various taxonomies. This approach ensures compatibility with established green finance standards while avoiding vendor lock-in.
        </p>
